or whatever.

08:57.060 --> 08:58.420
What do you think?

09:00.140 --> 09:07.340
<i>Well, I think that</i> there's a lot
more to makin' a cop than just paper.

09:09.110 --> 09:13.643
Yes... but I just...
thought it was unusual.

09:13.693 --> 09:15.049
It is.

09:16.740 --> 09:20.668
